Hierarchical Alignment (HAL) Format API (ALPHA version)
Copyright (C) 2012 by Glenn Hickey (hickey@soe.ucsc.edu)
Released under the MIT license, see LICENSE.txt

Dependencies:
https://github.com/benedictpaten/sonLib
http://www.hdfgroup.org/HDF5/ (with C++ API)
http://doxygen.org/ (for documentation)

Documentation:
make doxy

Build:
make

Use:
link to lib/halLib.a
include lib/hal.h

included Tools:
halStats - basic information about .hal file
halCons - conservation statistics 
hal2maf - MAF export

Import from Progressive Cactus:
https://github.com/glennhickey/cactus2hal


